@Use.Application.Service_HostAddress = http://localhost:5155

# Dev identity headers (no real auth yet). In Development these can be omitted
# and a deterministic local dev user is used instead.
@X-User-Email = local.dev@use.local

### Ask a question (new chat — chatSessionId omitted/null creates a session)
POST {{Use.Application.Service_HostAddress}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Email: {{X-User-Email}}

{
  "question": "Kedy je naplánovaný update systému Humanet pre mesiac August?",
  "chatSessionId": null
}

### Continue an existing chat (paste a chatSessionId from a previous response)
POST {{Use.Application.Service_HostAddress}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Email: {{X-User-Email}}

{
  "question": "A čo september?",
  "chatSessionId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### List the current user's chat sessions
GET {{Use.Application.Service_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions
X-User-Email: {{X-User-Email}}

### Create an empty chat session
POST {{Use.Application.Service_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Email: {{X-User-Email}}

{
  "title": "My new conversation"
}

### Get messages for a session (must be owned by the current user)
GET {{Use.Application.Service_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/messages
X-User-Email: {{X-User-Email}}

### Rate a RAG answer by ragQueryLogId (preferred — returned on the chat response)
POST {{Use.Application.Service_HostAddress}}/api/chat/rag-query-logs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/rating
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Email: {{X-User-Email}}

{
  "rating": -1,
  "feedback": "The answer used the wrong source page."
}

### Rate a RAG answer by chat message id (user or assistant message)
POST {{Use.Application.Service_HostAddress}}/api/chat/messages/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/rating
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Email: {{X-User-Email}}

{
  "rating": 1
}

###
